Package: ReducedExperiment
Type: Package
Title: Tools for investigating dimensionally reduced expression data
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Jack", "Gisby", , "jackgisby@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0511-8123"))
Description: A toolbox for reducing the dimensionality of expression data and
    analysing the decomposed data. Provides utilities for independent component
    analysis (ICA) and weighted gene correlation network analysis (WGCNA).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
